MatchedRegions.transcript: Hi, my name is Ryan from the Singapore University of Technology and Design, and today I'll be presenting a paper, Matrix Multiplicative Weights Updates in Quantum Zero-Sum Games, Conservation Laws and Recurrence.

MatchedRegion.Text: Matrix Multiplicative Weights Updates in Quantum Zero-Sum Games

MatchedRegions.transcript: This paper is joint work with Rahul Jain from the National University of Singapore, as well as Georges Pillares from the Singapore University of Technology and Design.
